==English==
===Verb===
'''will do'''
# ''Future tense of'' [[do]].
#: ''Who '''will do''' the dishes?''

===Expression===
'''Will do.'''

# [[affirmative|Affirmative]] [[yes]] in response to an especially personal or direct request for the performance of some action.
#: ''Could you wake me when you get up? — '''Will do'''.''
#: ''Make sure you understand this before the next class. — '''Will do'''.''